{"type": "article", "id": 3834, "title": "Trunkster无拉链旅行箱", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-25T08:48:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233354hgxd2i0kKw6VqJ83.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t纽约创业团队 Trunkster 日前带来一款智能旅行箱，从外观上来看，这款旅行箱最特别的地方在于其无拉链的设计，设计团队为其安装了一个更加便利的推拉式上盖，方便用户取用以及放入各种物品，免去在狭小空间内还要打开旅行箱上盖才能取用物品的烦恼。此外，Trunkster 还配有一个可拆卸的移动电源与内部称重系统，用户只需要拎起旅行箱便可看到箱体显示屏上的重量。最重要的是，Trunkster 自带 GPS 定位系统，对于丢三落四的用户来说是非常贴心的设计呢。目前，Trunkster 正在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/trunkster/trunkster-zipperless-luggage-with-gps-battery-scal\" target=\"_blank\">Kickstarter </a>上众筹，起售价 600 美元，预计明年 8 月出货。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233353NPUZCnTVrEyOzYl0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233353slcUCQaYMbTeu5XB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"http://e.fastcompany.net/multisite_files/fastcompany/imagecache/inline-large/inline/2014/11/3038858-inline-i-1-the-perfect-high-tech-carry-on-has-no-zipper-at-all.gif\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}